anks</p>\r\n',0,'','','',1,'','','',0,0,'Asia/Tokyo','','2020-12-22 22:33:27','2020-11-04 22:27:05',0),
(12,28,'i-will-design-a-remarkable-app',0,800,3,'USD',1,'10','Mobile,app design',4,'<p><strong>Before Starting</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Please clearly indicate the number of pages of your app/website.</li>\r\n	<li>It would be great if you have a wireframe output. If not, determine your needs by comparing competitor apps.</li>\r\n	<li>If the price/page balance in my gig doesn&#39;t fit you, I&#39;ll send a special offer.</li>\r\n	<li>I&#39;m not doing a free sample page and competitor analysis. You must first order.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>I&#39;m open to signing NDA</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Why should we work together?&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1) 100% unique &amp; high-quality mobile app design. (Please check my portfolio below &amp;&nbsp;<em>you will love it.</em>)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2) Perfectly working apps on iOS and Android</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3)&nbsp;<strong>Figma</strong>&nbsp;source file, all necessary assets, and&nbsp;<strong>code output</strong>&nbsp;for development. (yay!)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4)&nbsp;<u>Fast and timely work delivery.&nbsp;</u>(I&#39;m good at that.)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5) You will definitely have an app that you will fall in love with it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6) Good communication and 100% customer satisfaction.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7) You will have a user experience oriented design. You will understand what this means in your sales and interaction with the user.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8) My difference from others is that I graduated from university with honors and you will be working with&nbsp;<strong>an award-winning professional designer.&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please read the&nbsp;FAQ.&nbsp;below ;) Have more questions?&nbsp;<strong>I&#39;m here! feel to write...</strong></p>\r\n',0,NULL,'','',0,'','','',0,0,'Asia/Tokyo','','2020-11-05 07:35:18','2020-11-04 22:35:18',0),
(13,28,'i-will-design-professional-company-website-for-you',0,15,5,'USD',1,'3','Web design',2,'<p>Hello!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI&#39;m Naqi, a professional&nbsp;<strong>Front-End Developer, UI Designer &amp; Illustrator.</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nI&#39;ve been working on the Digital Graphics Industry for 4 years, with clients from all over the world.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn this gig,&nbsp;<strong>I will design a beautiful and unique UI for your website or app.</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong>I can design from a homepage or a landing page to a website with 5+ pages or even your mobile app. I don&#39;t use themes or pre-made templates, all are handcrafted.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>I&#39;ll deliver to you:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A unique and custom UI design</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>All Sketch source files of your projects</li>\r\n	<li>and 5 stars rated service!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>To start, I&#39;ll need from you:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Your business name and information (What do you do?)</li>\r\n	<li>Your logo/brand identity (logotype, colors, fonts, etc)</li>\r\n	<li>A brief description of what you need</li>\r\n	<li>Examples and references of websites you really like</li>\r\n	<li>Websites of your competitors</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n',0,NULL,'','',1,'','','',0,0,'Asia/Tokyo','','2020-11-05 07:37:09','2020-11-04 22:37:09',0),
