ayment from you outside the Website. As a Freelancer,<br />\r\nyou agree to notify Smoothworks.net immediately if your Employer seeks to pay<br />\r\nyou outside the Website. If you are aware of a breach of the foregoing prohibitions,<br />\r\nor any potential circumvention of the Smoothworks Billing and Payment Services,<br />\r\nplease submit a confidential report to Smoothworks.net by Freelancer Portal Chat<br />\r\nor <span style=\"color:#0000ee\">contact us.</span> <br />\r\n6. <span style=\"font-size:12pt\">Agreement to Pay: </span>If, for any reason, Smoothworks.net does not receive payment<br />\r\nfor any amounts that you have authorised to be paid through your use of the<br />\r\nSmoothworks Billing and Payment Services, you agree to pay such amount<br />\r\nimmediately upon demand by Smoothworks.net. You also agree to pay any interest<br />\r\ncharges, attorneys&#39; fees and other costs of collection incurred by<br />\r\nSmoothworks.net in collecting from you, the authorised but unpaid amount. In<br />\r\nsuch case, Smoothworks.net may, at its option, stop processing any further<br />\r\npayments made by you and apply any amounts then held by Smoothworks.net on<br />\r\nyour behalf toward any deficiencies, losses or costs that we have incurred as a<br />\r\nresult of your use of the Smoothworks Billing and Payment Services. We may also<br />\r\nmake appropriate reports to credit reporting agencies, financial institutions, tax<br />\r\nagencies and law enforcement authorities, and cooperate with them in any<br />\r\nresulting investigation or prosecution. <br />\r\nResolution Service<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14pt\">(A) Eligibility</span><br />\r\nSmoothworks.net offers the Resolution Service to those Registered Users that have funds<br />\r\nin SmoothPay and requested Smoothworks.net to assume all or a portion of the payment<br />\r\nliability for services and who are engaged in a dispute over a Job that is (i) Pursuant to a<br />\r\nJob posting b